def handToDice(hand):
    firstDigit = hand // 100
    secondDigit = (hand % 100) // 10
    thirdDigit = (hand % 100) % 10
    return firstDigit, secondDigit, thirdDigit

def diceToOrderedHand(a, b, c):
    Largest = max(a,b,c)
    Smallest = min(a,b,c)
    Medium = a + b + c - Largest - Smallest
    return Largest * (10)**2 + Medium * 10 + Smallest
